        "MasterPrompt":  "2x2 grid, do this for 4 intricate types of traditional Lanna handmade crafts from Northern Thailand{composition: “Hybrid UI / 3D Toy Photography”theme:1. “Lanna Umbrella Painting (Bo Sang Umbrella Craft)”2. “Traditional Lanna Wood Carving”3. “Northern Thai Silver Hammering Craft”4. “Lanna Textile Weaving”background: “Seamless white cyclorama”z_axis_layers:foreground_floating:type: “2D Flat Black Vectors”content: “Semantic Inference: Traditional artisan tools used for each Lanna craft style — carving chisels, umbrella brushes, weaving looms, silver hammer tools, thread spools, bamboo frames, floral motifs”midground_3D:type: “Matte Vinyl Toy”content: “Lanna artisan working at a wooden craft desk creating each traditional Northern Thai craft, stylized toy-like proportions”character_design: “Semantic Inference: Traditional Northern Thai artisan fashion — indigo mor hom clothing, woven textiles, traditional Lanna accessories, relaxed artisan workshop aesthetic”background_floating_top:type: “2D Graphic Design”content: “Row of 4 polaroid-style cards featuring inferred Lanna craft motifs + text labels — floral umbrella patterns, carved temple motifs, silver tribal patterns, woven textile geometry”background_right:type: “3D Object”content: “Premium product display box matching each Lanna craft aesthetic with traditional Northern Thai pattern systems and warm handmade artisan branding”}",
