        "MasterPrompt":  "THEME: เทศกาลร่มบ่อสร้าง - ศิลปะร่มล้านนาแห่งเชียงใหม่POPUP_ELEMENTS: A large hand-painted Bo Sang umbrella with intricate floral Lanna patterns, bamboo frames, colorful paper parasols in various sizes, artisans painting umbrellas, and miniature dancers in traditional Northern Thai attire holding decorative umbrellasBACKGROUND_ART: Misty Chiang Mai landscape with gentle mountains and rural village scenery in an ink-wash style, featuring subtle silhouettes of wooden houses and temple rooftopsVERTICAL_BANNERS: Distressed paper strips with elegant Thai calligraphy, Lanna-inspired patterns, and gold-edged ornamental detailsCOLOR_PALETTE: Vermilion Red, Marigold Yellow, Teal Blue, and Natural Bamboo BeigeBASE_TEXTURE: An old Northern Thai folklore book resting on a finely woven bamboo mat (เสื่อกก) with subtle Lanna textile patternsTASK:Create a professional Thai pop-up book poster in a vertical composition, combining traditional Thai papercraft art, cultural storytelling, and modern editorial graphic design.[CORE VARIABLES]- THEME: [USER_INPUTS.THEME][AESTHETIC \u0026 STYLE]- Style: Intricate 3D pop-up papercraft, miniature diorama aesthetic, blending digital 3D rendering with traditional Thai ink-wash and Lanna art- Quality: Hyper-detailed, crisp paper-cut edges, visible paper layers, subtle cardstock thickness, soft shadows, warm cultural and festive atmosphere- Colors: Dominant [USER_INPUTS.COLOR_PALETTE] with parchment/off-white accents- Lighting: Soft top-down studio lighting combined with warm sunlight glow to enhance depth, color vibrancy, and layered shadows[COMPOSITION — LAYERED SYSTEM]1. THE FOUNDATION (Lower Third)- An open, weathered antique book with [USER_INPUTS.BASE_TEXTURE], placed on a traditional woven bamboo mat- The surface beneath includes subtle Lanna motifs and floral decorative patterns- From the book pages, a dimensional miniature festival scene emerges upward2. THE 3D POP-UP WORLD (Middle Focus)- Centerpiece: [USER_INPUTS.POPUP_ELEMENTS] emerging from the book with visible handcrafted paper textures- Movement: Flowing umbrella rotations, fabric motion, and dynamic arrangement suggesting a lively cultural festival- Vertical structure: [USER_INPUTS.VERTICAL_BANNERS] rising behind the scene, layered with depth, featuring refined Thai calligraphy and gold-accented edges3. THE CULTURAL BACKDROP (Upper Tier)- Background: [USER_INPUTS.BACKGROUND_ART]- Atmospheric depth: soft mist, warm daylight gradients, and layered mountain silhouettes- Additional elements: faint temple rooftops, village scenery, and cultural ambiance integrated subtly into the background[TYPOGRAPHY RULES — CRITICAL]- Thai text must be 100% correct in spelling, grammar, and cultural context- Use only authentic Thai language for all visible text- No garbled characters, no mixed scripts, no incorrect tone marks- Thai calligraphy must be elegant, readable, and culturally appropriate- Do not generate placeholder text or pseudo-Thai characters[STRICT CONSTRAINTS]- Single composition only, vertical 9:16 aspect ratio- Clean, minimalist, premium editorial layout with strong negative space- No clutter, no random decorative noise- Maintain visible papercraft realism (folds, layers, thickness)- No modern objects, no Western elements, no unrelated festivals- Do not generate any extra text beyond the designed Thai banners and calligraphy",
