        "MasterPrompt":  "“Ultra-clean modern editorial infographic. The topic is Lemongrass Drink (น้ำตะไคร้) routine. Base all visuals, colors, objects, mood, ingredients, and steps entirely on this topic.Hero visual: a stylized flat-lay or floating arrangement of 3–4 iconic objects associated with lemongrass drink — fresh lemongrass stalks, a clear glass of pale golden herbal tea, sliced pandan leaves, and a small pot — slightly angled or in soft perspective, glowing subtly. All elements arranged dynamically around the hero in a non-restrictive editorial layout.Ingredients Section: Label it ‘What You Need’ — include 6–8 relevant items with small icons or emoji illustrations next to each, with a practical quantity or duration written like a recipe:* 🌿 Lemongrass stalks — 4–5 stalks (cut and crushed)* 💧 Water — 1 liter* 🍯 Palm sugar — 2–3 tbsp* 🧂 Salt — a pinch* 🍋 Lime juice — 1 tbsp (optional)* 🌱 Pandan leaves — 2 leaves (tied knot)* 🧊 Ice — 1 cup (for serving)* 🍶 Honey — 1 tbsp (optional alternative sweetener)Steps Section: 5–6 numbered panels with arrows or connecting lines forming a logical flow, each with a short action label and small relevant icon, using glassmorphism or frosted card styling:1. 🔪 Prep — Cut and crush lemongrass stalks2. 💧 Boil — Add lemongrass and pandan into boiling water3. ⏱ Simmer — Let simmer for 10–15 minutes4. 🍯 Sweeten — Add sugar and a pinch of salt5. 🧃 Strain — Remove solids, pour into container6. 🧊 Serve — Add ice and optional lime juiceStats Badges: 4–5 floating pill-shaped badges showing relevant metadata, displayed as clean minimal bubbles near the hero:* ⏱ Prep Time: 5 min* 🔥 Cook Time: 15 min* 🌿 Herbal Level: 100% Natural* 🧊 Best Served: Chilled* 💪 Benefit: Refreshing \u0026 Digestive AidVisual Style: Use a fresh herbal palette — soft green, pale yellow, and warm beige tones. Clean white or light textured background with subtle grain. Bold modern sans-serif typography. Clean vector icons.Composition: Hero centered or slightly offset, ingredients on one side, steps opposite or below with connecting lines, stat badges as floating pills, generous negative space.Lighting: Soft natural studio lighting with a refreshing, calm tone. Premium editorial aesthetic, social-feed optimized. Ultra-crisp. No watermark.”",
