        "MasterPrompt":  "“Create an infographic image of Khanom Jeen Nam Ngiao, combining a realistic photograph or photoreal render of the object with technical annotation overlays placed directly on top.Use black ink–style line drawings and text (technical pen / architectural sketch look) on a pure white studio background, including:•Key component labels (fermented rice noodles, Nam Ngiao broth, minced pork, tomatoes, dried cotton tree flowers, blood cubes, chili paste, herbs)•Internal cutaway or exploded-view outlines (layering of noodles, broth, toppings, garnishes)•Measurements, dimensions, and scale markers (portion size, bowl diameter, ingredient ratios)•Material callouts and quantities (ingredients and approximate weights/volumes)•Arrows indicating function, force, or flow (broth absorption, flavor infusion, heat/steam direction)•Simple schematic or sectional diagrams where relevant (assembly of the dish from base to topping)Place the title “KHANOM JEEN NAM NGIAO” inside a hand-drawn technical annotation box in one corner.Style \u0026 layout rules:•The real object remains clearly visible beneath the annotations•Annotations feel sketched, technical, and architectural•Clean composition with balanced negative space•Educational, museum-exhibit / engineering-manual vibeVisual style:Minimal technical illustration aesthetic, black linework over realistic imagery, precise but slightly hand-drawn feel.Color palette:White background, black annotation lines and text only. No colors.Output:1080×1080, ultra-crisp, social-feed optimized, no watermark.”",
