        "MasterPrompt":  "Create a high-resolution vertical 3D character illustration in a stylized Pixar-meets-designer-toy aesthetic.Main character:“Lanna Soul Kitchen” — depicted as a tall, slim, slightly exaggerated Pixar-style 3D character inspired by a traditional Northern Thai (Lanna) chef.The character should embody the identity of a master Lanna street-food and cultural cuisine artisan.Maintain iconic visual elements of Northern Thai culinary culture:- traditional indigo mor-hom clothing- handwoven pha khao ma fabric- rolled sleeves- wooden cooking utensils- charcoal-grill atmosphere- calm but skillful chef postureTranslate all features into clean, simplified, blocky designer-toy proportions with soft sculpted geometry.The character must remain immediately recognizable as a Lanna chef culture icon, shown in full-body view with expressive personality and warmth.Pose:Use a natural but expressive stance.The chef may:- hold a traditional Northern Thai cooking spoon- present a bowl of khao soi- adjust a charcoal grill- carry a woven basket of herbs- stand proudly with calm confidenceHead angle, hand gesture, and posture should communicate hospitality, craftsmanship, and cultural pride.Background:Automatically choose a vivid, bold, high-saturation solid color inspired by Northern Thai culinary identity.Recommended tones:- spicy chili red- turmeric yellow- smoky orange- herbal green- deep indigo- roasted charcoal brownThe background should feel flat, clean, graphic, and striking — like a luxury conceptual food-culture exhibition poster.Avoid gradients.Avoid dull cinematic gray.The floor may use a closely related tone with subtle reflective texture.The environment remains minimal, endless, and uncluttered.Lighting:Use one strong directional light source from one side or upper angle.This light should create a sharp, enlarged symbolic shadow behind the character.Lighting must feel graphic, dramatic, and intentional.Key Concept — Shadow as spiritual projection:The shadow behind the chef must NOT replicate the human body.Instead, the shadow becomes a symbolic projection of the “spiritual world” of Lanna cuisine and Northern Thai cultural identity.The shadow should transform into a surreal symbolic composition inspired by:- rising aromatic smoke- traditional Lanna patterns- flames from charcoal grilling- giant chili silhouettes- mortar and pestle forms- mountain contours of Northern Thailand- elephant motifs- temple roof silhouettes- swirling noodle forms- herbal leaves and spice cloudsThe shadow must visually embody:“LANNA SOUL KITCHEN”The symbolic shadow should feel poetic, cultural, emotional, and visually powerful.It must become the true conceptual core of the poster.Typography:Place the spiritual-world keyword as the main poster text:“LANNA SOUL KITCHEN”Use elegant minimalist typography:clean serif or modern sans-serif depending on mood.Place typography in a balanced poster composition, preferably top-left.Smaller secondary typography may include:“Northern Thai Chef”or“Chiang Mai Culinary Spirit”Rendering:Pixar-style 3D rendering with designer-toy influence:- matte textures- soft sculpted surfaces- simplified geometry- cinematic clarity- premium collectible-toy aesthetic- highly polished visual finishKeep the character stylized but recognizable as a Northern Thai culinary artisan.Use subtle texture or film grain only if it enhances warmth and atmosphere.Do not overload the composition with excessive props.Composition:Poster-like composition with strong negative space.The chef occupies one strong visual anchor area.The symbolic shadow occupies a larger visual field as the emotional and conceptual counterweight.The image should instantly communicate:this is not simply a chef portrait —it is a symbolic projection of Northern Thai culinary spirit and cultural identity.Mood:Iconic,warm,culturally intelligent,symbolic,editorial,emotionally memorable,premium gallery-poster aesthetic,balancing traditional craftsmanship with modern conceptual design.Aspect ratio:9:16 vertical.",
        "ExampleImage":  "https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?authuser=0\u0026sz=w800\u0026id=1q4xR3bGLJt7Cm44o5XZRO3Im8Dh6ZQsU",
        "Application":  "• สำหรับครูผู้สอน: ใช้เป็นแผนภาพข้อมูล (Infographic) ประกอบการสอนเรื่องสัดส่วนสารอาหาร โภชนาการ หรือพืชสมุนไพรในท้องถิ่น และสามารถให้ผู้เรียนฝึกแปลงสูตรอาหารในครัวเรือนออกมาเป็นแผ่นภาพกราฟิกเพื่อฝึกทักษะการสื่อสารและการคิดเชิงระบบ (Systems Thinking)   • สำหรับผู้บริหาร: นำโครงสร้างการจัดวางและรูปแบบภาพถ่ายนี้ ไปประยุกต์ใช้ในการจัดทำแผ่นพับหรือสื่อประชาสัมพันธ์ โครงการอาหารปลอดภัยในสถานศึกษา การนำเสนอผลิตภัณฑ์เด่นของโรงเรียน (School OTOP) หรือใช้ตกแต่งรายงานผลงานนวัตกรรมการบริการชุมชนของสถานศึกษา"
