        "MasterPrompt":  "USER INPUTGAME_TITLE: LANNA HERBAL RUSHMAIN_CHARACTER: แม่ค้าสาวชาวเหนือใส่ผ้าซิ่นลายล้านนา เสื้อพื้นเมืองสีเขียว และผ้ากันเปื้อนสีน้ำตาลGAME_ENVIRONMENT: ร้านขายน้ำสมุนไพรล้านนาริมทางใต้ร่มไม้ พร้อมป้ายไม้สไตล์พื้นเมืองITEM_THEME: ขวดน้ำสมุนไพร, ตะไคร้, อัญชัน, ใบเตย, มะตูม, แก้วไม้ไผ่, สมุนไพรแห้งPRIMARY_COLORS: Warm Herbal Green and Earthy OrangeTASK: Create a professional “2D Game Design Concept Sheet” presented in a 4-grid layout (2x2) based on the style of image_e087d1.jpg.[GRID COMPOSITION - 4 SEPARATE VIEWS]1. TOP-LEFT (Title \u0026 Main Gameplay): Display the game logo “[GAME_TITLE]” with a cinematic gameplay shot. Show [MAIN_CHARACTER] preparing and serving herbal drinks within the [GAME_ENVIRONMENT].2. TOP-RIGHT (Inventory \u0026 UI): A top-down view of the game’s inventory management system. Show a grid of various [ITEM_THEME] with clean UI labels, buttons, herbal recipes, and currency stats.3. BOTTOM-LEFT (World Navigation): A side-view or isometric view of the [GAME_ENVIRONMENT] featuring clickable world elements like local markets, herbal ingredient stalls, seating areas, lanterns, and NPC customers.4. BOTTOM-RIGHT (Truck/Loading Scene): A zoomed-in view of a delivery cart or herbal storage area being packed with [ITEM_THEME].[ART STYLE \u0026 AESTHETIC]* Visual Style: Cute 2D flat illustration with clean, bold outlines (Cartoon/Chibi style).* Aesthetics: High-quality, vibrant, cozy, and culturally inspired by Northern Thailand. The atmosphere should feel warm, friendly, and engaging.* Colors: Strictly apply [PRIMARY_COLORS] throughout all 4 panels to ensure brand consistency.[DETAILED ELEMENTS]* Character Design: [MAIN_CHARACTER] must look cheerful, welcoming, and expressive.* Environment: Include small charming details related to [GAME_ENVIRONMENT] such as hanging lanterns, bamboo furniture, woven baskets, tiny cats, tropical plants, and wooden Lanna decorative patterns.* UI Elements: Labels, icons, menus, herbal recipe cards, and currency counters should look professional and “game-ready.”[STRICT CONSTRAINTS]* NO 3D rendering; must be 2D flat art.* The 4 grids must be clearly separated by thin black borders.* Keep the composition balanced and organized.* NO garbled text in the UI; keep it clean and intentional.",
