        "MasterPrompt":  "“Create a crisp clean infographic storyboard poster for HOW TO MAKE THAI MILK TEA. Wide 16:9 layout, white background, black borders, bold black typography, premium Pixar 3D rendering, bright vivid colors — polished tea-making station, bright café kitchen, warm orange Thai tea, silver tea pot, condensed milk cans, clear plastic cups, crushed ice.Top header:•HOW TO MAKE THAI MILK TEA•TOTAL VIDEO TIME: 15 SECONDS•8 PANELS · BREW · MIX · SERVESame character throughout:A cheerful Thai café vendor in their early 30s, wearing a rolled-sleeve brown apron, black T-shirt, dark trousers, and casual café shoes. Bright clean café counter environment, warm daylight mixed with soft indoor lighting throughout. One tea-making station against the wall — stainless steel kettle, tea filter sock, condensed milk cans, sugar jar, clear plastic cups, and ice bucket. The Thai tea mixture is always a vivid orange tea blend prepared in the same station setup throughout every panel.\n8 panels:Panel 1 — THE SETUPWide shot. The café vendor standing confidently behind the tea counter preparing ingredients. Tea leaves, condensed milk, sugar, and ice neatly arranged. Caption: “Every great Thai tea starts here.”Panel 2 — THE BREWMedium shot. Hot water being poured dramatically through a traditional Thai tea sock filter into a silver pot. Bright orange tea flowing smoothly. Steam rising beautifully. Caption: “Brew the tea strong.” Sound: boiling water, soft café ambience.Panel 3 — THE POURClose-up on the tea stream only. The vivid orange Thai tea pouring through the filter into the pot with elegant motion. Rich color saturation and steam visible. Caption: “Slow pour. Deep flavor.” Sound: liquid pouring softly.Panel 4 — THE MIXMedium shot. Vendor adding condensed milk and sugar into the tea while stirring with a long spoon. Cream swirling into the orange tea creating beautiful patterns. Caption: “Sweet and creamy.” Sound: spoon clinking against metal.Panel 5 — THE ICEMedium shot from the side. Large scoop of crushed ice dropping into a tall clear plastic cup. Ice scattering dynamically with tiny water droplets flying. Caption: “Fill with ice.” Sound: sharp ice crackling.Panel 6 — THE FINAL POURClose-up on the final serving moment. Bright Thai milk tea cascading into the ice-filled cup creating rich creamy gradients. Condensed milk drizzling elegantly on top. Caption: “Pour to perfection.” Sound: smooth liquid pour.Panel 7 — THE FINISHClose-up on the completed Thai milk tea. Plastic lid sealed perfectly, straw inserted, condensation visible on the cup. Beautiful orange-and-cream layers glowing under café lighting. Caption: “Ready to serve.” Sound: cup sealing click.Panel 8 — THE PAYOFFWide shot. The café vendor smiling proudly while handing the finished Thai milk tea to a happy customer across the counter. Warm café atmosphere, clean workspace, bright inviting lighting. Caption: “สดชื่นทุกแก้ว” Sound: soft café ambience and distant chatter.STYLE NOTES:Pixar 3D vivid rendering. Bright clean café lighting throughout — NO dark frames. Character consistent in every panel. Tea-making station identical in every panel — polished stainless steel surfaces, orange Thai tea, clear cups, ice bucket, café environment.”",
