        "MasterPrompt":  "“2x2 grid, do this for 4 iconic Chiang Mai foods: Input = Subject  Subjects = Khao Soi, Sai Ua (Northern Thai sausage), Nam Prik Noom with vegetables, Sticky Rice with Mango (Northern style presentation)Function Render_Wooden_Peg ($Subject)  Anchor:[Wooden Toy $Subject] :: [Handcrafted Peg Doll]::5  Morphology:  $Subject with simplified shapes, rounded forms, child-friendly proportions, visible wood grain, turned on a lathe, hand-painted food details::4  Material Physics:  Sanded Linden wood, beech wood, safe water-based paint (matte), tactile warmth, natural handcrafted imperfections::3  Illumination:  Warm sunlight, cozy atmosphere, soft shadows highlighting the wood grain and soft colors::2  Render Stack:  Macro Photography, 8k, shallow depth of field, Waldorf / Montessori aesthetic, soft neutral background::1  Composition:  Arrange all 4 subjects in a clean 2x2 grid layout, evenly spaced, minimal and calm visual balance  Negative:  Plastic, metal, hyper-realistic textures, glossy surfaces, dark tones, industrial style:: -1”",
