        "MasterPrompt":  "[MASTER PROMPT — NEO-TRADITIONAL THAI MURAL ART V.1]TASK: Create a Neo-Traditional Thai Mural Art illustration based on the scene theme of students learning mathematics in a traditional Thai educational setting. The artwork must perfectly emulate the flat 2D style of classic Thai temple murals mixed with vintage historical fashion.ART STYLE \u0026 RENDERING (STRICT)* Overall Aesthetic: 2D flat illustration, neo-traditional Thai mural painting (จิตรกรรมฝาผนังประยุกต์).* Linework: Clean, precise, and continuous ink outlines defining all shapes.* Shading/Texture: Smooth, flat gouache and watercolor textures. NO heavy 3D rendering, NO realistic shadows, NO digital plastic look.* Facial Features: Characters must have classical Thai mural faces (serene expressions, elegantly curved arched eyebrows, almond-shaped eyes, smooth stylized anatomy, graceful curved fingers/hands).COMPOSITION \u0026 ELEMENTS* Feature 4–5 characters standing or sitting in a calm, organized arrangement, interacting through a learning activity.* Scene Theme: Studying mathematics — students engaging with counting, measuring, and problem-solving using traditional methods.* Dress them in historical Thai attire, including Chong Kraben and Sabai, with subtle variations to indicate roles (teacher and students).* Integrate props such as palm-leaf manuscripts, chalk slates, counting tools, abacus-like objects, and geometric drawing instruments naturally into their hands or immediate surroundings.* Use a color palette of muted earth tones, indigo blue, soft ochre, and gold accents for garments and props.BACKGROUND RULE* Keep the background strictly plain and isolated (off-white or subtle watercolor paper grain).* DO NOT generate elaborate environments or architectural scenes. Focus entirely on the characters and their interaction.RESTRICTIONS (ABSOLUTE)* STRICTLY NO typography, NO text, NO numbers, and NO characters of any kind.* NO watermarks, NO signatures, NO logos.* NO photorealism. Maintain the 2D traditional illustrated art style.Creative Direction:Emphasize calmness, wisdom, and cultural continuity. The scene should reflect learning as a timeless human activity, blending mathema",
