        "MasterPrompt":  "Ultra-premium cloisonné enamel collectible fridge magnet displayed inside a bright, high-end store window, vertical 9:16.Text on the product:“CHIANG MAI · THAILAND”Shape:– custom silhouette based on Wat Phra That Doi Suthep outline (temple + mountain form)– tall vertical composition to emphasize height– polished metallic gold frameFocal point:– Wat Phra That Doi Suthep dominating the composition (70–80% height)– highly detailed and visually iconicScene inside the magnet:– Ping River flowing at the base– Historic Chiang Mai Gate in the foreground– Chiang Mai old city skyline behind– Doi Suthep in the distance– Lanna temple architecture and traditional elementsMiniature workers (key element):– tiny craftsmen painting the surface– workers on ladders painting details– one worker near the top of the main temple– small figures interacting with the environmentInteraction:– floating lanterns inspired by Yi Peng Festival– reflections interacting with surfaces– slight imperfections for realismMaterials:– cloisonné enamel (glossy translucent colors)– embossed metallic outlines– handcrafted textureColor palette:– PRIMARY: warm gold / saffron– SECONDARY: deep green / forest tone– ACCENT: lantern orange glow– subtle metallic highlightsEnvironment (important):– bright modern store interior– light wood or marble surfaces– glass reflections from display window– blurred background with shelves and products– optional: people in background slightly out of focusLighting:– soft natural daylight– warm indoor lighting mix– realistic reflections and shadowsStyle:– hyper-realistic product photography– miniature world feeling– extremely rich in micro-details for zoom– premium collectibleTechnical:– 85mm lens– shallow depth of field– 8K ultra-detailed– highly shareable",
