        "MasterPrompt":  "USER_INPUT  PROJECT_NAME: Historic Chiang Mai Gate Cultural Center  STYLE: Contemporary Lanna Monumentalism — สถาปัตยกรรมล้านนาร่วมสมัยผสมความสง่างามของกำแพงเมืองเชียงใหม่และซุ้มประตูประวัติศาสตร์  MATERIAL: อิฐแดงเชียงใหม่ หินทรายสีอุ่น ไม้สักล้านนา และกระจกใสสมัยใหม่  PHILOSOPHY: ศูนย์กลางวัฒนธรรมล้านนาและประตูสู่ประวัติศาสตร์เชียงใหม่  DIMENSIONS: 4000 FEET LONG / 280 FEET TALL  LIGHTING: warm lantern-inspired architectural glow with subtle golden evening illumination  ASPECT_RATIO: 16:9  PROMPTTASK  Create a professional Architectural Design Board in a vertical ASPECT_RATIO composition, presenting a massive monumental structure based on PROJECT_NAME.CORE GOAL  - The final image must feel like a high-end architectural presentation board.  - The building must look realistically massive, monumental, symmetrical, and professionally designed.  - The board must combine cinematic renders, technical elevation, night render, blueprint, and data panels in one vertical layout.  - The result must feel like a premium architecture studio proposal inspired by Northern Thai heritage, not a fantasy poster.POSTER LAYOUT — VERTICAL STACK1. TOP PANEL — CINEMATIC AERIAL  - Show a wide-angle panoramic rendering of PROJECT_NAME during golden hour sunset.  - The building must be perfectly symmetrical.  - Clearly communicate the immense scale defined by DIMENSIONS.  - Show the full monumental structure inspired by Historic Chiang Mai Gate and Chiang Mai Old City walls, including grand plazas, reflecting pools, landscaped courtyards, and ceremonial pathways.  - Integrate subtle Lanna architectural geometry and historic gate symbolism into the design.  - The composition should feel epic, balanced, and cinematic.2. MIDDLE PANEL — TECHNICAL ELEVATION  - Show a clean architectural orthographic projection from the side view.  - Use a neutral dark background.  - Include professional technical labels for major architectural sections.  - Labels may include:    - Main Cultural Axis    - Grand Lanna Archway    - Heritage Gallery Wing    - Glass Atrium    - Reflecting Courtyard    - Cultural Exhibition Hall    - Public Plaza    - Lantern Garden  - Include scale markers and subtle measurement lines.  - Keep this section precise, minimal, and technical.3. LOWER-MID PANEL — NIGHT RENDERING  - Show the same panoramic architectural view as the top panel, but at night.  - Use LIGHTING to highlight warm lantern-inspired illumination, Lanna roof silhouettes, red brick textures, elegant arches, glazing reflections, and monumental symmetry.  - The structure should feel calm, ceremonial, monumental, and culturally luxurious.  - Keep the night render elegant and cinematic, not overly dramatic.4. BOTTOM PANEL — DATA \u0026 BLUEPRINT  Divide this section into three parts:Left:  - Infographic panel listing technical details:    - Style: STYLE    - Dimensions: DIMENSIONS    - Material: MATERIAL    - Structural specifications    - Cultural design philosophy  - Use clean architectural typography.Center:  - A detailed 2D top-down blueprint or floor plan of the building.  - Show symmetry, ceremonial axis, entrance gates, courtyard geometry, public circulation, garden rhythm, and monumental structural balance.Right:  - A circular or oval inset showing a close-up perspective of the main entrance inspired by Historic Chiang Mai Gate.  - Include the motto: PHILOSOPHY  - The entrance should show:  - red-brick craftsmanship  - carved Lanna wood detailing  - monumental arch scale  - lantern lighting  - human-scale reference figures  - refined contemporary cultural architectureARCHITECTURAL STYLE \u0026 DETAIL  - Core aesthetic: STYLE.  - The structure should reinterpret Historic Chiang Mai Gate into a monumental contemporary cultural megastructure.  - Blend:  - historic Chiang Mai fortification geometry  - Lanna temple roof rhythm  - modern civic architecture  - symmetrical ceremonial planning  - contemporary museum-scale spatial design- The architecture must feel structurally believable and buildable.  - Avoid fantasy castle aesthetics.MATERIALITY  - Use MATERIAL as the primary surface system.  - Red brick should feel tactile, historic, and warm.  - Teak wood should feel handcrafted and premium.  - Glass should feel contemporary and elegantly integrated into the historical-inspired structure.  - Materials should respond naturally to sunset and night illumination.ENVIRONMENT  - Surround the building with:  - ceremonial plazas  - reflecting pools  - lantern gardens  - symmetrical pathways  - tropical Northern Thai landscaping  - subtle mountain silhouettes in the distance  - public gathering spaces- The environment must emphasize the building’s monumental civic scale and cultural significance.TYPOGRAPHY \u0026 BRANDING  - Display PROJECT_NAME at the top in a sophisticated wide-spaced serif font.  - Use clean minimalist monospace or sans-serif fonts for labels, data, dimensions, and technical annotations.  - Typography must feel editorial, architectural, and premium.  - Avoid excessive text clutter.TEXT ACCURACY  - All visible text must be clean, readable, and intentional.  - No garbled text.  - No random fake labels.  - If typography becomes unstable, reduce text quantity and keep only the title, major labels, and essential data.STYLE \u0026 RENDERING  - Professional architectural visualization quality.  - Octane-render aesthetic.  - 8K detail.  - Realistic material behavior.  - Sharp technical clarity.  - Premium editorial architectural-board composition.  - Balanced contrast between cinematic render panels and technical sections.STRICT CONSTRAINTS  - No messy layout.  - No garbled typography.  - No random labels.  - No asymmetrical design.  - No weak sense of scale.  - No fantasy palace look.  - No chaotic sci-fi megacity.  - No low-detail rendering.  - No generic architecture.  - No cluttered infographic layout.  - No unrealistic material behavior.  - The building must feel monumental, symmetrical, and culturally grounded in Chiang Mai heritage.OUTPUT  - Single image.  - Architectural presentation board following ASPECT_RATIO.  - Four stacked sections:  1. cinematic aerial sunset render    2. technical elevation    3. night render    4. data + blueprint + entrance inset  - Premium architecture studio proposal quality.FINAL INTENT  Create a complete architectural design board for a monumental Historic Chiang Mai Gate-inspired cultural megastructure, combining cinematic beauty, technical precision, realistic materiality, and contemporary Northern Thai architectural identity i",
