        "MasterPrompt":  "\"objective\": \"Create a minimalist editorial poster of [LOCATION_NAME] where the map itself is composed of colorful anime-inspired imagery reflecting [LOCAL_IDENTITY] identity.\",\"prompt\": \"A minimalist vertical poster featuring the full map outline of [LOCATION_NAME] on a clean white background, but instead of standard terrain, the entire landmass is constructed from densely arranged colorful anime-inspired visuals blended with subtle [CULTURAL_STYLE] cultural motifs. The shape of [LOCATION_NAME] is clearly recognizable from a distance, while up close the surface is made of layered vibrant anime-style faces, silhouettes, expressive eyes, dramatic hair shapes, manga textures, action lines, and colorful character fragments integrated with hints of [LOCAL_IDENTITY] identity such as [SPECIFIC_CULTURAL_ELEMENTS]. Use vivid saturated colors across the anime collage, including [COLOR_PALETTE_LIST], while keeping the overall poster elegant and refined. The map should feel visually rich and colorful, but still organized and premium rather than chaotic. Add soft shadows so the map feels slightly raised from the white background. Place the word \u0027[LOCATION_UPPERCASE]\u0027 in thin modern uppercase typography near the upper left, with the [LOCAL_LANGUAGE] text \u0027[LOCAL_LANGUAGE_NAME]\u0027 beneath it. The overall image should feel like a luxury design print combining modern cartography, anime-inspired visual culture, and [LOCAL_IDENTITY] identity, clean, sparse, visually striking, and highly detailed.\",\"style\": {\"medium\": \"editorial poster design\",\"aesthetic\": \"minimalist art poster with colorful anime-collage map infused with [CULTURAL_STYLE] identity\",\"background\": \"clean matte white\",\"lighting\": \"soft studio lighting with subtle depth and shadow\",\"color_palette\": [\"[COLOR_1]\",\"[COLOR_2]\",\"[COLOR_3]\",\"[COLOR_4]\",\"[COLOR_5]\",\"[COLOR_6]\",\"[COLOR_7]\",\"white\"],\"typography\": \"thin modern sans-serif, elegant and minimal\"},\"composition\": {\"orientation\": \"vertical poster\",\"layout\": \"large negative space with the [LOCATION_NAME] map placed to the right side\",\"text_placement\": \"title and [LOCAL_LANGUAGE] text at upper left\"},\"details\": {\"map_features\": [\"full [LOCATION_NAME] outline\",\"clearly recognizable geographic shape\",\"surface made from colorful anime-inspired faces, silhouettes, and manga-like details blended with [CULTURAL_STYLE] cultural elements\",\"[GEOGRAPHIC_FEATURES] subtly reflected\",\"soft shadow beneath the map\"],\"visual_effect\": [\"readable as [LOCATION_NAME] from afar\",\"bright colorful anime collage visible up close\",\"artistic layered composition\",\"balanced detail without clutter\"],\"annotations\": [\"[LOCATION_UPPERCASE]\",\"[LOCAL_LANGUAGE_NAME]\"]},\"constraints\": [\"Keep the overall design minimalist and premium\",\"The map must remain clearly recognizable as [LOCATION_NAME]\",\"The anime-inspired elements should form the map itself, not sit around it\",\"Subtly integrate [LOCAL_IDENTITY] cultural identity\",\"Make the anime elements colorful and vibrant\",\"Use clean white negative space\",\"Avoid a busy poster layout\"],\"negative_prompt\": [\"specific copyrighted characters\",\"dull monochrome colors\",\"washed-out palette\",\"messy collage\",\"cluttered background\",\"random floating anime figures outside the map\",\"dark background\",\"political borders\",\"satellite map\",\"heavy text clutter\",\"low detail\",\"generic shape with no [LOCATION_NAME] identity\"],\"output_format\": {\"aspect_ratio\": \"4:5\",\"resolution\": \"high\"}}",
