        "MasterPrompt":  "[USER INPUT]CITY_OR_COMMUNITY: หมู่บ้านหัตถกรรมบ้านบ่อสร้าง จังหวัดเชียงใหม่ (Bo Sang Handicraft Village, Chiang Mai)MAIN_TOPIC: วิถีชีวิตหัตถกรรมร่มกระดาษสาและการท่องเที่ยวเชิงวัฒนธรรมKEY_MESSAGE: \"อนุรักษ์ภูมิปัญญาร่มบ่อสร้าง สร้างชุมชนสร้างสรรค์อย่างยั่งยืน\"MAIN_FACILITIES: ศูนย์หัตถกรรมร่มบ่อสร้าง, เวิร์กช็อปทำร่มกระดาษสา, ถนนคนเดิน, ร้านงานฝีมือท้องถิ่น, ลานเทศกาลร่มบ่อสร้างLOCAL_IDENTITY: ร่มกระดาษสาหลากสี, บ้านไม้ล้านนา, ต้นลำไย, จักรยานท่องเที่ยว, โคมล้านนา, งานเพ้นท์ร่มด้วยมือWORKER_OR_PEOPLE: ช่างทำร่ม, นักท่องเที่ยว, แม่ค้าในตลาด, ศิลปินเพ้นท์ร่ม, เด็กนักเรียนเรียนงานหัตถกรรมINFO_SECTIONS: 1. ประวัติร่มบ่อสร้าง 2. งานหัตถกรรมท้องถิ่น 3. การท่องเที่ยวชุมชน 4. วัฒนธรรมล้านนาLANGUAGE: Thai only[PROMPT]Create a friendly isometric educational infographic map about [MAIN_TOPIC] in [CITY_OR_COMMUNITY].[CORE CONCEPT]Design a large illustrated community map that explains how [MAIN_TOPIC] supports everyday life in [CITY_OR_COMMUNITY]. The image should feel informative, warm, clean, and easy to understand, like a public-service poster, municipal brochure, school textbook diagram, or community education board.[MAIN MAP ILLUSTRATION]Create a colorful isometric town landscape showing [CITY_OR_COMMUNITY] from an elevated bird’s-eye view. Include roads, houses, small buildings, greenery, water features, local infrastructure, and everyday community activity. Integrate [MAIN_FACILITIES] clearly into the map as the main functional elements. Add [LOCAL_IDENTITY] naturally throughout the landscape so the place feels locally rooted and recognizable.[PEOPLE \u0026 ACTIVITY]Show small simplified people throughout the town performing everyday actions related to [MAIN_TOPIC]. Include [WORKER_OR_PEOPLE] interacting with the facilities, walking, working, maintaining infrastructure, learning, farming, traveling, or participating in community life. The people should be small, friendly, readable, and evenly distributed across the scene.[INFOGRAPHIC SIDE PANEL]Add a clean vertical information panel on the left side of the image. Divide it into multiple rounded rectangular boxes based on [INFO_SECTIONS]. Each box should contain small icon illustrations with short labels in [LANGUAGE]. The side panel should feel organized, educational, and visually connected to the main map.[TEXT \u0026 TYPOGRAPHY]Include a clear headline at the top explaining [KEY_MESSAGE]. Use [LANGUAGE] for all visible text, labels, signs, and annotations. Typography should be neat, rounded, friendly, and suitable for a public education infographic. Text should be integrated into the design, not randomly floating.[VISUAL STYLE]- Isometric educational illustration- Clean vector-like drawing- Soft pastel colors- Friendly civic infographic style- Rounded shapes and readable icons- Thin clean outlines- Slightly hand-drawn warmth- Clear visual hierarchy- Bright but not overly saturated colors- Public-service brochure aesthetic- School textbook illustration mood[COMPOSITION]- Wide horizontal layout- Large main isometric map on the right or center- Organized information panel on the left- Headline and short message at the top- Balanced spacing between map, icons, labels, and text- Many small details, but still clean and readable- Keep the layout educational, not chaotic[COLOR PALETTE]Use a soft, cheerful civic color palette with umbrella reds, pastel yellows, sky blues, soft creams, warm browns, gentle greens, and muted Lanna-inspired accent colors. The overall color feeling should be fresh, clean, artistic, and community-friendly.[DETAILS TO INCLUDE]- Traditional Lanna wooden houses- Umbrella workshops and market streets- Roads, bicycles, small bridges, and walking areas- Trees, gardens, decorative lanterns, and local scenery- Public facilities related to [MAIN_TOPIC]- Workers or community members- Small tuk-tuks or local transport elements when relevant- Informational icons in the side panel- Clear labels and signage in [LANGUAGE][STRICT CONSTRAINTS]- NO photorealism- NO 3D CGI rendering- NO dark cinematic lighting- NO messy crowded composition- NO overly complex unreadable text- NO random fantasy elements- NO dramatic perspective distortion- NO harsh shadows- NO corporate stock-photo style- Keep the design friendly, educational, clean, and highly readable[FINAL INTENT]Create a polished isometric community infographic map that clearly explains [MAIN_TOPIC] in [CITY_OR_COMMUNITY], combining a detailed town illustration, local identity elements, small human activities, educational side panels, friendly icons, and clear typography in [LANGUAGE].",
