        "MasterPrompt":  "A breathtaking vintage-style travel poster of Chiang Dao District, Chiang Mai, Thailand during a magical golden-hour sunset. In the foreground, a young female traveler stands on a rustic wooden bridge overlooking the peaceful countryside, with her back facing the viewer. She wears a wide straw hat, soft cream cardigan, long flowing floral skirt, and a brown leather backpack. Beside her rests a classic vintage bicycle surrounded by blooming wildflowers and lush Northern Thai greenery.The district of Chiang Dao is filled with iconic Northern Thai wooden houses, traditional Lanna-style architecture, cozy countryside cottages, rice fields, and beautifully maintained gardens. The majestic Chiang Dao Mountain rises dramatically in the background with mist drifting across the forested slopes. A calm river flows through the landscape, crossed by charming bamboo and wooden bridges. Small walking paths wind between local homes, cafés, and rice paddies while visitors peacefully explore the scenery. Dense tropical forests and towering limestone mountains surround the district in the background.The sky is vibrant blue with glowing golden clouds and a few birds soaring overhead. Warm cinematic sunlight bathes the entire landscape, creating dreamy reflections on the water and illuminating the traditional Lanna houses with a cozy amber glow. Rich natural greenery, colorful flowers, and serene countryside atmosphere create a fairytale-like Northern Thai mountain paradise.Highly detailed, ultra-realistic, cinematic composition, nostalgic vintage tourism poster aesthetic, cozy fantasy realism, HDR lighting, vibrant colors, symmetrical framing, peaceful wanderlust mood, 4k quality.At the bottom, large bold retro typography reads:“CHIANG DAO”“CHIANG MAI”“NORTHERN THAILAND MOUNTAIN DISTRICT”Style: vintage Thai tourism poster, ultra-detailed photorealism, cinematic golden-hour lighting, cozy countryside atmosphere, postcard aesthetic, timeless travel advertisement design.",
