        "MasterPrompt":  "Hyper-realistic 3D infographic poster of a one-day tourist route, created based on a single input: [LAMPHUN].The system strictly focuses on the inner regions of [LAMPHUN], automatically identifying the country, culture, and the actual urban layout of Lamphun.A one-day route is being created, designed from morning to evening.The route starts from a well-defined starting point, which is also:1 (START)(e.g., Wat Phra That Hariphunchai)From this point, the system generates an optimized one-way route connecting 5–8 major historical and tourist attractions within the city.Route logic (CRITICAL)The route should follow the real navigation path (based on actual streets)Only moving forward — no turning back, no re-visiting areasThe stream naturally passes through neighboring neighborhoodsEffective progression, just like on a real mapFinal stop = strong finale (sunset spot, riverside, cultural space)Map designThe city is presented as a highly detailed 3D relief map:* Real street network* Area structure* Topography and river system (e.g., Ping River if visible)On a clean light gray studio background.The route is shown as a continuous glowing line from 1 → N.Each stop includes:* Numbered icon (1 = START)* Hyper-detailed miniature 3D model of the landmark* Local area detail (enhanced microscale study)Each landmark is clearly labeled (e.g., Ku Chang Ku Ma, Wat Chammathewi)Daily Flow Layer (IMPORTANT)Each stop reflects the progression of the time of day:* Morning start (temple / local market)* 2–3: Cultural + historical exploration* 4–5: Midday highlights / local food zone* 6–7: Scenic or relaxed areas* Final stop: Sunset / evening riverside or cultural atmosphereOptional: subtle lighting transitions (morning → warm sunset tones)Localized city elementsInclude only Lamphun-specific objects around the map:* Local food (e.g., Lamphun Longan)* Cultural symbols (Lanna architecture, lanterns)* Traditional lifestyle elements(Exclude generic travel items such as suitcases or compasses)Route Panel* Ordered list 1 → N* Place name* 3–5 word description* Optional duration* Category iconAdditional elementsA small folded Thai flag appears in the corner (automatically detected).Heading“ONE DAY IN LAMPHUN”or“LAMPHUN DAILY ROUTE GUIDE”StyleUltra-realistic 3D rendering, premium editorial infographic style, soft studio lighting, global illumination, shallow depth of field, clean minimalistic layout.All text in English.",
