        "MasterPrompt":  "Ultra-premium vertical propaganda poster, A4 size. Subject: a legendary Thai prince-poet warrior with flowing dark hair, elegant royal garments inspired by classical Siamese literature, and calm yet deeply burdened eyes carrying wisdom, sorrow, and unshaken resolve. A sacred flute rests in his hand — not merely an instrument, but a force capable of altering fate itself.UPPER HALF — SILHOUETTE DOUBLE EXPOSURELarge dramatic silhouette of the prince’s head and upper torso, face angled slightly off-center. Flowing hair, royal sash, and drifting fabric extend outward forming the dominant visual mass. Within the silhouette, apply a cinematic double-exposure collage:A colossal mystical sea spirit emerges from within — part ocean wave, part celestial guardian — its luminous form overlapping the prince’s face like a spirit bound to his destiny. Behind it: vast oceans, storm-torn islands, ancient Siamese palace silhouettes, and distant temple spires dissolve into the mid-zone. Swirling musical energy streams, drifting flute melodies visualized as glowing wave-like ribbons, and layered action vignettes are woven throughout — a lone ship crossing violent seas, a mermaid reaching upward from moonlit waters, a young warrior standing against a giantess shadow. Floating artifacts drift through the composition: seashells, broken royal scrolls, lotus petals, ancient maps, and fragments of shattered coral.Internal gradient: warm sunset gold → deep royal crimson → moonlit indigo → oceanic sapphire blue, glowing outward from a luminous spiritual core.LOWER HALF — ANCHORING FULL-BODY FIGUREFull-body Phra Aphai Mani in a grounded forward-moving stance along a storm-lit shoreline. One hand gently raises the enchanted flute, releasing visible streams of luminous musical energy into the air. His long royal cloak — ivory white with flowing gold-patterned hems inspired by Thai mural art — moves dramatically in the sea wind behind him. Expression: calm, reflective, tragic, yet unwaveringly destined.CENTRAL ENERGY AXISA vertical luminous stream of musical and oceanic energy connects the full-body figure at the base through rising light particles, flowing melody lines, and glowing sea mist into the silhouette collage above. This spiritual axis represents fate, memory, and the eternal echo of legend — structural, not decorative.FLANKING ELEMENTSLeft side at 25% opacity: soft mist-blended silhouettes of allies and companions — a mermaid figure, a loyal young prince, a wandering sailor — dissolving warmly into ocean haze.Right side at 25% opacity: cold abstract antagonist presence — towering giantess shadows, cursed sea storms, fractured palace ruins, and dark ocean currents dissolving into negative space.STYLETraditional Thai mural aesthetics fused with cinematic anime illustration and Eastern sumi-e ink wash. Ink diffusion edges on all silhouette boundaries. Soft blur transitions between layered memories and ocean depth. Fragmented parchment texture overlays. Layered atmospheric sea mist, drifting musical particles, and glowing wave haze. Controlled white negative space used as compositional breathing space.Lighting: high-contrast focal source illuminating the prince’s face and enchanted flute. Secondary cold rim lighting suggests the supernatural ocean spirit presence emerging from behind.COLORGlowing sunset gold and sacred amber for musical energy. Deep sapphire blue and luminous indigo for oceanic spiritual force. Charcoal ink-black shadows with softened edges. Metallic gold highlights inspired by Thai lacquer art. White glowing melody particles and pale seafoam mist throughout. Desaturated teal atmosphere layers mixed with warm sepia memory tones.TYPOGRAPHYTop: a small faded Thai royal seal or literary emblem resembling an ancient Siamese manuscript stamp.Bottom: one bold wide-tracked word — “LEGEND” or “DESTINY” — with a thin subtitle line beneath in elegant serif typography.TONEEpic, poetic, cinematic, and mythological. This is not merely a literary character illustration — it is a visual biography of a man whose music shaped kingdoms, crossed oceans, and carried both love and sorrow through eternity. It should feel timeless, melancholic, spiritual, and quietly triumphant.",
        "ExampleImage":  "https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?authuser=0\u0026sz=w800\u0026id=1hLkhtcc0Uxgxaw0Czkz1rsxad5fKa9m9",
        "Application":  "• สำหรับครูผู้สอน: นำภาพผลลัพธ์ไปประยุกต์ใช้เป็น สื่อกระตุ้นการคิด (Thinking Tools) สื่อประกอบการสอนแบบตั้งคำถาม (Inquiry-based Learning) นำแผ่นภาพโครงสร้างไปทำโมเดลกระดาษสามมิติ หรือทำการ์ดกิจกรรมประกอบแอปพลิเคชันการจัดทำแผนการสอนเพื่อพัฒนาทักษะการวิเคราะห์เชิงลึกของผู้เรียน   • สำหรับผู้บริหาร: ใช้เป็นแนวทางต้นแบบในการส่งเสริมให้ครูผู้สอนพัฒนาสื่อนวัตกรรมการเรียนรู้ที่ทันสมัย สอดคล้องกับแนวคิดนวัตกรรมการศึกษา (Learning Innovation) และสามารถนำสไตล์การจัดสรุปข้อมูล (เช่น โครงสร้าง Infographic หรือพิมพ์เขียว) ไปใช้จัดทำแผนภาพยุทธศาสตร์การพัฒนาคุณภาพของโรงเรียนเพื่อนำเสนอต่อผู้ทรงคุณวุฒิหรือหน่วยงานต้นสังกัด"
