        "MasterPrompt":  "A high-end, diptych-style promotional poster in a realistic, detailed Thai-anime illustration style inspired by classic Thai literature and luxury editorial fashion campaigns.The left panel features พระอภัยมณี (Phra Aphai Mani) in a refined three-quarter pose, looking calm yet charismatic. He wears a luxurious deep indigo traditional-modern Thai formal suit that blends royal Siamese tailoring with contemporary high-fashion structure, enriched with intricate gold embroidery inspired by Rattanakosin floral motifs and ocean-wave patterns. He elegantly holds his magical flute in one hand. Behind him rests a ceremonial travel ensemble inspired by ancient Thai epic adventures, including a sheathed royal sword and decorative journey ornaments. The left panel includes a refined flute-emblem logo, elegant typography reading:“THE MELODY — OF THE OCEAN SAGE —”Below appears:“PHRA APHAI MANI”along with a beautifully typeset excerpt inspired by his literary philosophy about wisdom, compassion, music, and destiny.The right panel features นางเงือก (The Mermaid / Nang Ngueak) in a dramatic close-up profile portrait with soft cinematic side lighting and elegant emotional expression. Her flowing hair subtly transitions into ocean-wave textures with delicate pearl and coral ornamentation. She wears an elegant black-and-deep-teal Thai couture dress with luxurious gold embroidery inspired by marine motifs and classical Thai decorative art. Her jewelry includes a shell-shaped royal emblem pendant symbolizing the sea kingdom.The right panel includes a refined ocean-shell insignia logo with typography reading:“THE VIGIL — OF THE TIDAL HEART —”Below appears:“NANG NGUEAK”along with a poetic literary-style quote about devotion, sacrifice, and eternal love across worlds.OVERALL DESIGN:* Both panels share a premium warm ivory background with subtle marble-paper texture and faint Thai manuscript patterns* Unified editorial luxury-poster layout* Shared elegant footer typography:    “Sunthorn Phu”    “PHRA APHAI MANI EST. 1822”CENTER HEADER:Between the two characters, centered elegantly across both panels:“FATE \u0026 DESTINY”rendered in luxurious gold Thai-calligraphy-inspired script typography with subtle embossed texture.STYLE:realistic detailed anime illustration,luxury Thai editorial poster,premium cinematic character art,high-fashion Thai literature reinterpretation,elegant gold-accent composition,refined Thai fantasy aesthetic,soft cinematic lighting,ultra-detailed embroidery and textile rendering,balanced negative space,collector-edition anime poster qualityCOLOR SYSTEM:* Left panel (Phra Aphai Mani): royal indigo, antique gold, deep ocean blue* Right panel (Nang Ngueak): black teal, pearl white, muted emerald, warm gold accents* Shared background: warm ivory marble textureTEXT QUALITY — EXTREMELY IMPORTANT:* all typography must be perfectly readable* elegant editorial spacing* no broken characters* no distorted Thai or English typography* premium luxury-brand typography layoutMOOD:mythological romance,elegant literary drama,timeless Thai epic reinterpretation,luxurious emotional atmosphere,calm but powerful heroic presence,premium collector-poster aestheticOUTPUT:* ultra-high-resolution diptych poster* print-ready* symmetrical luxury composition* highly detailed anime realism* premium publishing-quality artwo:::",
