        "MasterPrompt":  "Search the web for detailed information about Chom Thong District, Chiang Mai, Thailand — including its history, geography, Doi Inthanon National Park, agricultural culture, architecture, temples, climate, local traditions, tourism significance, population, and surprising lesser-known details.Then create a dramatic editorial infographic poster about Chom Thong District in the style of a National Geographic environmental and cultural feature — but focused on landscape, culture, and architecture.CORE VISUAL CONCEPT:Chom Thong District becomes the full-bleed atmospheric hero of the composition:* a photorealistic cinematic render combining Doi Inthanon mountain scenery, terraced rice fields, misty forests, Northern Thai temples, local villages, waterfalls, and morning atmosphere* the landscape fills the entire poster top-to-bottom* layered environmental depth with clouds, mountain haze, forest textures, rivers, and temple silhouettes* dramatic natural lighting inspired by real Chiang Mai dawn and rainy-season atmosphere* no empty background areasEDITORIAL OVERLAY SYSTEM:* Text and infographic overlays float organically over the scenery like premium National Geographic editorial spreads* No boxed magazine layout* No rigid grid* Information layers should feel naturally integrated into the environment* Use semi-transparent dark moss-green, earth-brown, or mist-grey panels inspired by Chom Thong’s natural paletteTYPOGRAPHY:* Oversized bold typography dominates the upper portion:“CHOM THONG”* Subtitle below:    “อำเภอจอมทอง • เชียงใหม่ • THAILAND”* Typography style:    bold editorial serif mixed with elegant modern sans-serif,    luxury documentary aesthetic,    high readability,    cinematic placement integrated into the landscapeMAIN LANDSCAPE HERO:* Doi Inthanon as the visual anchor* Include:    * twin pagodas near the summit    * mist-covered mountain ridges    * rice terraces    * Wachirathan waterfall atmosphere    * local Karen hill tribe cultural references    * Northern Thai temple rooftops    * rural agricultural roads and villages* Everything should feel naturally connected rather than collage-likeANNOTATED CALLOUTS:Add elegant editorial callout lines pointing directly toward:* the twin royal pagodas* rice terraces* cloud forest ecosystem* local temple architecture* waterfalls* agricultural valleys* high-altitude forest zonesFLOATING DATA PANELS:Use layered infographic overlays covering:* district establishment history* elevation and climate data* Doi Inthanon summit height* agricultural economy* annual tourism statistics* biodiversity significance* UNESCO or conservation relevance if applicable* 3 surprising lesser-known facts about Chom ThongSURPRISING FACTS SECTION:Include visually integrated editorial facts such as:* Doi Inthanon being Thailand’s highest mountain* rare cloud forest biodiversity* strong Karen cultural heritage* unique cool-climate agriculture in Northern Thailand* seasonal sea-of-mist phenomenonMAP \u0026 INFOGRAPHIC ELEMENTS:* small inset map showing Chom Thong’s location within Chiang Mai Province and Northern Thailand* icon-based stats row including:    * elevation    * climate    * visitor numbers    * forest coverage    * waterfalls    * agriculture* subtle topographic contour graphics blended into the backgroundPULL QUOTE:Include one bold editorial pull quote integrated into the environment:“Where Thailand touches the clouds.”COLOR SYSTEM:The entire palette must be extracted naturally from Chom Thong itself:* rainforest green* mist grey* rice-field gold* wet stone charcoal* earthy brown* cool mountain blue* soft sunrise amberLIGHTING \u0026 MOOD:cinematic but natural,misty mountain dawn,humid atmospheric depth,National Geographic documentary realism,immersive environmental storytelling,dense tactile realism,rich environmental moodSTYLE:photorealistic editorial infographic,National Geographic-inspired architectural + environmental feature,luxury travel-documentary poster,cinematic landscape realism,organic layered infographic design,dense but readable information hierarchy,premium publication-quality compositionRESTRICTIONS:* no white background* no clean magazine grid* no flat infographic style* no isolated panels* no cartoon look* no sci-fi aesthetics* no generic tourism brochure layout* no empty negative space* no simplistic vector renderingOUTPUT:* single vertical 4:5 poster* ultra-high-resolution* dense cinematic editorial composition* print-ready* tactile layered infographic realism* full-bleed environmental storytelling aesthet:::",
