        "MasterPrompt":  "Create a stylized illustration of Phra Aphai Mani from the classic Thai epic literature Phra Aphai Mani.Character DirectionAnalyze the character’s canon personality and translate it into a clear visual archetype: calm, intelligent, poetic, mysterious, and spiritually powerful.Identify the character’s signature visual palette inspired by royal Siamese aesthetics, oceanic mythology, ivory flute tones, indigo night seas, and antique gold ornamentation. Use these as the dominant visual accents throughout the artwork.Pose \u0026 MovementDesign a pose that instantly communicates the character’s nature:calm yet commanding presence, standing with graceful balance while playing the magical flute, flowing garments reacting to wind and mystical sound waves, controlled movement with hidden power and emotional depth.Facial ExpressionKeep the expression fully aligned with the character’s emotional identity and literary personality:wise eyes, composed confidence, subtle melancholy, refined elegance, and mystical charisma.Visual StyleAnime-inspired illustration mixed with contemporary Thai streetwear fashion and graphic poster aesthetics.Use crisp linework, semi-flat rendering, bold contrast, and a polished modern finish while preserving Thai cultural identity.CompositionVertical 3:4 poster layoutCharacter positioned slightly off-centerStrong diagonal composition created through flowing flute energy, garments, and ocean wind movementForeground/background layering to create depthOutfit RedesignTransform the original royal Siamese costume into a modern techwear/streetwear interpretation while preserving recognizable Thai literary silhouette cues:flowing layered fabrics,contemporary Lanna-Siam fusion tailoring,ornamental metallic accessories,traditional Thai textile motifs,and a redesigned mystical flute as the centerpiece accessory.Color DirectionPredominantly white backgroundDeep indigo blue and antique gold as the primary signature accentsAdditional complementary accents using sea green or muted coral redMinimal but striking high-contrast paletteBackground DesignAbstract geometric poster-style backdrop with clean negative space.Incorporate subtle visual motifs inspired by:ocean waves,Thai mural patterns,celestial symbols,conch-shell spirals,and mystical sound-wave geometry from the enchanted flute.Effects \u0026 MotionAdd stylized motion streaks, ink-like energy waves, drifting petals, ocean mist, glowing flute resonance trails, and graphic accents matching the character’s mystical aura and royal literary identity.LightingDirectional cinematic lighting with sharp shadows and a soft indigo-gold glow using the signature accent tones.RenderingUltra-clean vector-inspired rendering, poster-grade composition, highly detailed, sharp 4K finish.",
