        "Recipe":  "• เนื้อหา/เป้าหมายบทเรียน [SUBJECT]: ขั้นตอนการทดลอง วัฏจักรธรรมชาติ หรือสรุปเนื้อหาบทเรียน   • รูปแบบและสไตล์ศิลปะ [STYLE]: Modern Editorial / Clean Minimal Vector Icons   • โครงสร้างการจัดวาง [LAYOUT]: Structured Layout with numbered panels and stats badges",
        "MasterPrompt":  "Create an ultra-detailed hyper-realistic cinematic miniature world map of [COUNTRY_NAME], designed as a premium luxury travel-poster masterpiece.COUNTRY_NAME: ThailandLANGUAGE_MODE: BILINGUALCAPITAL_CITY: BangkokICONIC_LANDMARKS: Grand Palace, Wat Arun, Wat Phra Kaew, Maya Bay, Doi Suthep Temple, Ayutthaya Historical Park, Giant Swing, Railay Beach, Sukhothai Historical Park, Chiang Mai Old CityNATURAL_FEATURES: tropical islands, turquoise Andaman Sea, limestone cliffs, lush rice terraces, dense northern mountains, waterfalls, floating markets, jungle forests, Mekong River, coconut beachesCULTURAL_IDENTITY: Thai street food culture, tuk-tuks, long-tail boats, Muay Thai, Songkran Festival, floating lanterns, elephant culture, golden temples, night markets, silk weaving, tropical fruit markets, Lanna architectureLanguage mode:Use LANGUAGE_MODE for all visible text in the image.If LANGUAGE_MODE is ENGLISH, use English for the country title, tagline, labels, and infographic details.If LANGUAGE_MODE is LOCAL_LANGUAGE, use the country’s local language or writing system for all visible text.If LANGUAGE_MODE is BILINGUAL, show the main country title in both English and the local language, with labels and infographic details using a balanced bilingual layout.If LANGUAGE_MODE is NO_TEXT, do not include any readable text, labels, typography, captions, or infographic words. Communicate everything visually through icons, symbols, landmarks, composition, and non-readable graphic marks.Core concept:Render the entire country as a massive handcrafted floating island civilization suspended in soft atmospheric clouds. The country should feel like a complete miniature world, combining geography, cities, culture, infrastructure, nature, landmarks, and storytelling into one cohesive visual composition.World structure:Show highly detailed terrain elevation across the country. Include visually rich mountains, forests, rivers, coastlines, waterfalls, deserts, lakes, farmland, villages, urban zones, and region-specific natural environments based on the country’s real geography.Blend natural beauty with modern development, historical heritage, and national identity. The island should feel geographically believable, densely layered, immersive, and highly zoomable.Regional identity:Every major region should feel visually unique and culturally alive. Represent different cities, provinces, or regions through distinct architecture, atmosphere, colors, traditions, and landscape identity.Integrate ICONIC_LANDMARKS naturally into the environment. Historical or cultural regions should feature appropriate monuments, temples, castles, mosques, churches, shrines, traditional districts, markets, or iconic structures where relevant.Natural regions should reflect the country’s authentic environmental identity through NATURAL_FEATURES.Capital city:Feature CAPITAL_CITY as a vibrant cinematic metropolis. Show realistic skyline details, glowing streets, dense urban storytelling, transportation systems, public spaces, and visually rich infrastructure.The capital should feel energetic, modern, important, and visually connected to the overall country composition.Infrastructure and movement:Include highways, railways, bridges, ports, airports, tiny moving vehicles, airplanes, trains, ferries, ships, and boats where appropriate.The miniature world should feel active and alive with small-scale movement, realistic transport systems, and subtle environmental storytelling details throughout the country.Cultural details:Integrate CULTURAL_IDENTITY subtly throughout the landscape. Add details related to food culture, transportation, festivals, regional symbols, wildlife, traditional clothing, markets, street life, music, sports, technology, national identity, and everyday life when relevant.These details should feel naturally embedded into the miniature world, not added as disconnected icons.Typography and information design:If LANGUAGE_MODE is not NO_TEXT, use a clean, minimal, luxury editorial typography layout.Place bold oversized “[COUNTRY_NAME]” typography prominently within the composition. The font style should feel inspired by the country’s identity and culture.Add a cinematic tagline near the main title. Add elegant minimal labels for major cities and landmarks, integrated naturally into the environment.Include refined information details showing population, language, currency, tourism, famous exports, cultural influence, technology, cuisine, and transportation systems where appropriate.Keep all typography clean, premium, readable, and visually integrated.If LANGUAGE_MODE is NO_TEXT, replace labels and information text with clean icons, visual symbols, and non-readable graphic marks.Visual style:Hyper-detailed miniature world aesthetic, cinematic travel-documentary mood, premium luxury travel poster design, high-detail environmental realism, satellite-inspired terrain readability, bright elegant presentation, emotionally immersive composition, and highly zoomable micro-details everywhere.Lighting and color:Use vibrant natural colors inspired by COUNTRY_NAME. Apply premium cinematic color grading, realistic lighting behavior, atmospheric fog depth, cinematic cloud formations, and reflective environmental surfaces.Maintain strong depth layering, beautiful contrast, and visual richness without becoming chaotic.Composition:Use the most suitable composition for the subject and destination identity. The country island should be the dominant centerpiece.Create a strong visual hierarchy with a clear title area when LANGUAGE_MODE is not NO_TEXT, and a clean information detail area when LANGUAGE_MODE is not NO_TEXT.Keep rich micro-detail throughout the central landscape. The overall design should feel expensive, modern, timeless, polished, and instantly eye-catching.Do not force any specific aspect ratio.Strict constraints:NO fixed aspect ratioNO messy or cluttered information layoutNO generic flat map appearanceNO empty or under-detailed regionsNO random fantasy elements unrelated to the countryNO weak typography hierarchyNO dull or lifeless atmosphereNO unreadable text when text is requiredNO readable text when LANGUAGE_MODE is NO_TEXTKeep the image cinematic, culturally rich, emotionally powerful, and highly polishedFinal result:An 8K masterpiece travel-poster illustration of COUNTRY_NAME as a floating miniature world civilization, combining geography, culture, architecture, infrastructure, natural identity, famous landmarks, and national storytelling into one luxurious, hyper-detailed, cinematic visual experience.",
